headline: 3 Big Reasons to Love W. R. Berkley (WRB)
summary: Since July 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 96.5%. But one standout stock has nearly doubled the market - over the past five years, W. R. Berkley has surged 177% to $71.14 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 25.5% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 18%.
